{
  "stem": "8569.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My sister was still weak from the sickness.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And through the offices of Marta, she was given a job, which was to guard the door at night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And for that, she-- my sister received then a payment-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a cup of jam.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we were very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had jam.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so we ran to the market-- there was another market from the girls who were working in quote, 'Kanada.' This Kommando was called because Canada was supposed to be the richest country in the world.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And these girls were working in sorting of the effects from the transport.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they used to smuggle into the camp anything you can dream of, from silk stockings to silk underwear to, you know, whatever people use to take with them and they managed to smuggle into.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyway, we went to the market with our cup of jam and with a spoon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And for three spoons of jam, we got our first toothbrush.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then we couldn't understand how come the whole cup was only three spoons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then we became wise in commerce.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "What you do, you choose a smaller spoon, and you dilute the jam with water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "This way, you could get another toothbrush and two bras.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So those were the first purchases that we made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we became friendly with Marta.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was friendship that lasts until today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was another thing that happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a group of girls that used to get together, tell stories about each other, sing Hebrew songs, dream of Israel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, we lifted ourselves from the reality of the camp into the fantasy of our meetings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they became more real to us than the reality around us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In this--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
